data.description: Beautiful estate home on Oversized 1.2 acre In the Woodlands of Malbis is ready for your family to enjoy!   Upon entering the foyer, you are welcomed with soaring ceilings and detailed crown molding. Open floor plan flows smoothly between the kitchen, family room, and keeping room with 2 fireplaces downstairs. Gourmet kitchen offers high end Viking appliances, gas range, double oven, bar seating and breakfast area. Large pantry and custom cabinets provide abundant storage. The downstairs theater room features new leather reclining chairs with USB charging stations, surround sound and mini bar. Deluxe outdoor grilling station is the perfect compliment for the kitchen when entertaining large parties. The primary suite upstairs is where your dreams will come true.. with a lovely balcony overlooking the expansive fenced backyard, fireplace in the connecting morning room that leads to the most indulgent master bath! Unbelievable closets, spa features and loads of storage make this master suite a complete oasis for relaxation.  2 new air conditioners, triple car garage and 2 tankless water heaters, sprinkler system, custom fence + new fence with double gate for easy boat storage, and outdoor grilling station add to the countless upgrades this home has to offer. Freshly painted inside and out with upgraded landscaping, you will be wowed with the lovely, well maintained curb appeal of this home. 3 routers for seamless internet connection throughout the house, make working from home effortless and uninterrupted. This elegant, immaculate estate will truly impress with all the custom features it has to offer. Make an appointment to see it in person today!   Lease purchase and rental options available.     *(ANY/ALL UPDATES ARE PER SELLER). *LISTING BROKER MAKES NO REPRESENTATION TO SQUARE FOOTAGE ACCURACY. BUYER TO VERIFY.
